msgstr "关键规则："

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:79
msgid ""
"**Don't `use perry_runtime::*`**. perry-runtime's internals (NaN-box tags, "
"struct layouts) change between Perry releases. perry-ffi is the stable "
"contract."
msgstr "**不要使用 `use perry_runtime::*`**。perry-runtime 的内部实现（NaN-box 标签、结构体布局）会在 Perry 版本之间变化。perry-ffi 才是稳定的契约。"

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:82
msgid ""
"**Use `unsafe extern \"C\"` for any function that takes pointer args**. "
"`*const StringHeader` etc. require unsafe at the call site."
msgstr "**对接受指针参数的任何函数使用 `unsafe extern \"C\"`**。`*const StringHeader` 等类型在调用点要求 unsafe。"

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:84
msgid ""
"**Document `# Safety` for unsafe fns** — at minimum say \"the pointer must "
"be null or a Perry-runtime `<Header>`\"."
msgstr "**为 unsafe 函数编写 `# Safety` 文档** —— 至少要写明“该指针必须为 null 或一个 Perry-runtime `<Header>`”。"

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:86
msgid ""
"**Async returns `*mut Promise`**. Pattern: `JsPromise::new()` → "
"`spawn_blocking(move || { tokio::runtime::Handle::current().block_on(async "
"{...}); promise.resolve(...) })` → return `promise.as_raw()`."
msgstr "**异步返回 `*mut Promise`**。模式：`JsPromise::new()` → `spawn_blocking(move || { tokio::runtime::Handle::current().block_on(async {...}); promise.resolve(...) })` → 返回 `promise.as_raw()`。"

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:90
msgid "`src/index.ts`"
msgstr "`src/index.ts`"

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:92
msgid ""
"Declare the TypeScript surface user code imports. Bodies here only run under "
"V8 / Node fallback; Perry's compiler resolves the function calls directly to "
"the `js_*` symbols at link time, never executing the TS body."
msgstr "声明用户代码导入的 TypeScript 表面。这里的函数体仅在 V8 / Node 回退路径下运行；Perry 的编译器在链接时会直接将函数调用解析到对应的 `js_*` 符号，从不执行 TS 函数体。"

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:97
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"/**\n"
