msgstr "打 release tag"

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:201
msgid ""
"The scaffolded `.github/workflows/release.yml` builds prebuilt staticlibs "
"for x86_64 + aarch64 macOS/Linux + Windows on tag and attaches them to the "
"GitHub release. Add or remove targets in the workflow's `matrix` block as "
"needed."
msgstr "脚手架生成的 `.github/workflows/release.yml` 会在打 tag 时为 x86_64 + aarch64 macOS/Linux + Windows 构建预编译静态库，并将其附加到 GitHub release。可按需在 workflow 的 `matrix` 块中增删目标。"

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:206
msgid "npm publish"
msgstr "npm publish"

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:212
msgid ""
"The scaffolded `package.json` includes the right `files: [...]` list to "
"bundle `src/` + `Cargo.toml` + the README. If you also vendor the prebuilt "
"artifacts in the npm tarball, add them to the `files` block."
msgstr "脚手架生成的 `package.json` 已包含合适的 `files: [...]` 列表，会打包 `src/` + `Cargo.toml` + README。如果你还想把预编译产物一并放入 npm tarball，请将其加入 `files` 块。"

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:216
msgid "Two distribution models"
msgstr "两种发布模式"

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:218
msgid "There are two ways your users get the staticlib:"
msgstr "用户获取静态库的方式有两种："

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:220
msgid "Model"
msgstr "模式"

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:220
msgid "What ships in the npm tarball"
msgstr "npm tarball 中包含的内容"

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:220
msgid "Trade-off"
msgstr "权衡"

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:222
msgid "**Vendor prebuilts**"
msgstr "**随包提供预编译产物**"

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:222
msgid ""
"`src/`, `Cargo.toml`, AND `prebuilt/<target>/lib<name>.a` for every target"
msgstr "`src/`、`Cargo.toml`，以及每个目标的 `prebuilt/<target>/lib<name>.a`"

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:222
msgid ""
"Bigger npm tarball; install is fast (no compile); user doesn't need a Rust "
"toolchain"
msgstr "npm tarball 更大；安装很快（无需编译）；用户无需 Rust 工具链"

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:223
msgid "**Source-only**"
msgstr "**仅源码**"

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:223
msgid "`src/`, `Cargo.toml`, no prebuilts"
msgstr "`src/`、`Cargo.toml`，无预编译产物"

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:223
msgid ""
"Tiny tarball; first `perry compile` runs `cargo build --release` (slow); "
"user needs Rust"
msgstr "tarball 极小；首次 `perry compile` 会运行 `cargo build --release`（较慢）；用户需要 Rust"

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:225
msgid ""
"Vendoring is the friendlier default for npm consumers. Source-only makes "
"sense if your matrix is too big for one tarball or if you're publishing a "
"private wrapper to a small audience."
msgstr "对 npm 使用者来说，随包提供预编译产物是更友好的默认方案。仅源码模式适合矩阵过大无法装进单个 tarball，或者你只是向小范围受众发布私有封装的情况。"

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:229
msgid ""
"The manifest's `targets.<target>.prebuilt` field tells Perry where to find a "
"prebuilt for the user's compile target:"
msgstr "manifest 的 `targets.<target>.prebuilt` 字段告诉 Perry 在哪里查找用户编译目标对应的预编译产物："

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:237
#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:238
#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:239
msgid "\"prebuilt\""
msgstr "\"prebuilt\""

