msgid "`targets.<target>`"
msgstr "`targets.<target>`"

#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:145
msgid ""
"Per-target build configuration. The `<target>` key is one of: `macos`, "
"`ios`, `linux`, `windows`, `android`, `web`, `harmonyos`, `tvos`, `watchos`, "
"`visionos`. Simulator variants use the same key as their device counterpart "
"(`ios` covers both `ios-simulator` and `ios`)."
msgstr "针对特定目标的构建配置。`<target>` 键可为以下之一：`macos`、`ios`、`linux`、`windows`、`android`、`web`、`harmonyos`、`tvos`、`watchos`、`visionos`。模拟器变体使用与对应物理设备相同的键（`ios` 同时覆盖 `ios-simulator` 与 `ios`）。"

