#: src/ui/tray.md:3
msgid ""
"Perry ships a cross-platform system tray API on `perry/ui` (issue #490). The "
"same six functions work on every desktop target — macOS, Windows, Linux/GTK4 "
"— and link as no-ops on the mobile / embedded backends."
msgstr "Perry 在 `perry/ui` 上提供了一套跨平台的系统托盘 API(issue #490)。同样的六个函数在每一个桌面目标 —— macOS、Windows、Linux/GTK4 —— 上都能工作,并在移动端 / 嵌入式后端上以 no-op 形式链接。"

#: src/ui/tray.md:7
msgid ""
"The API is **handle-based** and free-function: build a tray with "
"`trayCreate(iconPath)`, attach a context menu built with the existing "
"`menuCreate` / `menuAddItem` API via `trayAttachMenu(tray, menu)`, and "
"register a left-click callback with `trayOnClick`."
msgstr "该 API 是 **基于句柄** 的自由函数式 API:用 `trayCreate(iconPath)` 构建一个托盘,用现有的 `menuCreate` / `menuAddItem` API 构建一个上下文菜单并通过 `trayAttachMenu(tray, menu)` 挂接,通过 `trayOnClick` 注册左键点击回调。"

#: src/ui/tray.md:14
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"// Build the tray BEFORE App() — the tray icon installs while the\n"
"// runtime is starting up, so it's already live when the main window\n"
"// appears.\n"
"const tray = trayCreate(\"\")  // empty path → \"●\" placeholder\n"
"traySetTooltip(tray, \"My App\")\n"
"\n"
"// Right-click (or left-click on macOS) opens the menu attached below.\n"
"const menu = menuCreate()\n"
"menuAddItem(menu, \"Show\", () => status.set(\"tray/show\"))\n"
"menuAddSeparator(menu)\n"
"menuAddItem(menu, \"Quit\", () => status.set(\"tray/quit\"))\n"
"trayAttachMenu(tray, menu)\n"
"\n"
"// Optional: left-click handler. On macOS the menu pops on left-click,\n"
"// so this fires only when no menu is attached. On Windows / Linux,\n"
"// left-click and the menu are independent — typical usage is\n"
"// \"left-click → show main window, right-click → menu\".\n"
"trayOnClick(tray, () => {\n"
"    status.set(\"tray/click\")\n"
"})\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/tray.md:37 src/platforms/windows-7.md:23 src/system/background.md:24
#: src/plugins/appstore-review.md:54
msgid "API"
msgstr "API"

#: src/ui/tray.md:41
msgid "`trayCreate(iconPath: string): Widget`"
msgstr "`trayCreate(iconPath: string): Widget`"

#: src/ui/tray.md:41
msgid ""
"Create the tray icon. `iconPath` is a filesystem path to a PNG (or `.icns` "
"on macOS, `.ico` on Windows). Pass `\"\"` to use a \"●\" placeholder."
msgstr "创建托盘图标。`iconPath` 是指向 PNG 文件(在 macOS 上为 `.icns`,在 Windows 上为 `.ico`)的文件系统路径。传入 `\"\"` 可使用 “●” 占位图标。"

#: src/ui/tray.md:42
msgid "`traySetIcon(tray, iconPath)`"
msgstr "`traySetIcon(tray, iconPath)`"

#: src/ui/tray.md:42
msgid "Hot-swap the icon image. Empty path is a no-op."
msgstr "热替换图标。空路径为 no-op。"

#: src/ui/tray.md:43
msgid "`traySetTooltip(tray, tooltip)`"
msgstr "`traySetTooltip(tray, tooltip)`"

#: src/ui/tray.md:43
msgid "Set the tooltip text shown on hover."
msgstr "设置悬停时显示的工具提示文本。"

#: src/ui/tray.md:44
msgid "`trayAttachMenu(tray, menu)`"
msgstr "`trayAttachMenu(tray, menu)`"

#: src/ui/tray.md:44
msgid ""
"Attach a context menu (built with `menuCreate` / `menuAddItem`). Right-click "
"— or left-click on macOS — opens the menu."
msgstr "挂接一个上下文菜单(由 `menuCreate` / `menuAddItem` 构建)。右键点击 —— 或在 macOS 上左键点击 —— 即可打开该菜单。"

#: src/ui/tray.md:45
msgid "`trayOnClick(tray, callback)`"
msgstr "`trayOnClick(tray, callback)`"

#: src/ui/tray.md:45
msgid ""
"Register a left-click handler. On macOS the menu pops on left-click, so this "
"only fires when no menu is attached; on Windows / Linux, left-click and menu "
"are independent."
msgstr "注册一个左键点击处理函数。在 macOS 上,菜单会在左键点击时弹出,因此该处理函数仅在未挂接菜单时触发;在 Windows / Linux 上,左键点击与菜单是相互独立的。"

#: src/ui/tray.md:46
msgid "`trayDestroy(tray)`"
msgstr "`trayDestroy(tray)`"

#: src/ui/tray.md:46
msgid ""
"Remove the icon. The handle stays valid (subsequent setters are no-ops) so "
"existing closures don't crash."
msgstr "移除该图标。句柄保持有效(后续的 setter 调用变为 no-op),以便已注册的闭包不会崩溃。"

#: src/ui/tray.md:48
msgid "Updating the Icon"
msgstr "更新图标"

#: src/ui/tray.md:50
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"// Hot-swap the icon. The path can be a PNG (every platform), .icns\n"
"// (macOS), or .ico (Windows). Empty path is a no-op.\n"
"traySetIcon(tray, \"./assets/tray.png\")\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

