#: src/ui/tray.md:68
msgid ""
"Icon appears top-right of the menu bar. Click auto-pops the attached menu. "
"Tooltip routes through the button's `toolTip`. PNG and `.icns` paths "
"supported. Icons are rendered as templates — single-color glyphs adapt to "
"light/dark mode."
msgstr "图标显示在菜单栏右上角。点击会自动弹出已挂接的菜单。工具提示通过按钮的 `toolTip` 路由。支持 PNG 与 `.icns` 路径。图标会作为模板渲染 —— 单色字形会自适应浅色/深色模式。"

#: src/ui/tray.md:69 src/ui/tray.md:84 src/system/background.md:87
msgid "**Windows**"
msgstr "**Windows**"

#: src/ui/tray.md:69
msgid "`Shell_NotifyIconW` + `TrackPopupMenu`"
msgstr "`Shell_NotifyIconW` + `TrackPopupMenu`"

#: src/ui/tray.md:69
msgid ""
"Icon appears in the notification area (bottom-right). Left-click → `onClick` "
"callback. Right-click → menu. PNG and `.ico` paths supported (PNG via "
"`LoadImageW` with `LR_LOADFROMFILE`). `trayCreate` must come after "
"`App({...})` since the tray reuses the main window's `WndProc`."
msgstr "图标显示在通知区域(右下角)。左键点击 → `onClick` 回调。右键点击 → 菜单。支持 PNG 与 `.ico` 路径(PNG 通过带 `LR_LOADFROMFILE` 的 `LoadImageW` 加载)。`trayCreate` 必须放在 `App({...})` 之后,因为托盘会复用主窗口的 `WndProc`。"

#: src/ui/tray.md:70
msgid "**Linux/GTK4**"
msgstr "**Linux/GTK4**"

#: src/ui/tray.md:70
msgid "StatusNotifierItem (KSNI) over D-Bus"
msgstr "通过 D-Bus 的 StatusNotifierItem(KSNI)"

#: src/ui/tray.md:70
msgid ""
"Works on KDE Plasma, GNOME-with-`appindicator`\\-extension, XFCE, Cinnamon, "
"MATE, Budgie, LXQt out of the box. Vanilla GNOME without the extension keeps "
"the service alive but the icon doesn't render — a one-line warning logs at "
"create time."
msgstr "在 KDE Plasma、装有 `appindicator` 扩展的 GNOME、XFCE、Cinnamon、MATE、Budgie、LXQt 上开箱即用。未安装该扩展的原版 GNOME 仍能保持服务存活，但图标不会渲染——创建时会输出一行警告日志。"

