"`\"unsupported-platform\"`."
msgstr "空操作桩 —— `geolocationGetCurrent` 立即用 `\"unsupported-platform\"` 触发 `onError`。"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:68
msgid "Promise wrapper"
msgstr "Promise 包装器"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:70
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"import { geolocationGetCurrent } from \"perry/system\";\n"
"\n"
"function getPosition(): Promise<{\n"
"  lat: number;\n"
"  lng: number;\n"
"  accuracy: number;\n"
"  timestamp: number;\n"
"}> {\n"
"  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n"
"    geolocationGetCurrent(\n"
"      (lat, lng, accuracy, timestamp) =>\n"
"        resolve({ lat, lng, accuracy, timestamp }),\n"
"      (msg) => reject(new Error(msg)),\n"
"    );\n"
"  });\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/system/geolocation.md:89
msgid "Image picker"
msgstr "图像选择器"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:91
msgid ""
"Present the native photo-library picker. The callback receives an array of "
"absolute filesystem paths the user selected; read bytes via "
"`fs.readFileSync(path)` if needed."
msgstr "呈现原生照片库选择器。回调接收用户选择的绝对文件系统路径数组；如有需要，可通过 `fs.readFileSync(path)` 读取字节。"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:95
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"import { imagePickerPick } from \"perry/system\";\n"
"\n"
"imagePickerPick(\n"
"  5,        // maxCount\n"
"  true,     // allowMultiple\n"
"  (paths) => {\n"
"    if (paths.length === 0) {\n"
"      console.log(\"user cancelled\");\n"
"    } else {\n"
"      for (const p of paths) {\n"
"        console.log(\"picked:\", p);\n"
"      }\n"
"    }\n"
"  },\n"
");\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/system/geolocation.md:113
msgid "`imagePickerPick(maxCount, allowMultiple, callback)`"
msgstr "`imagePickerPick(maxCount, allowMultiple, callback)`"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:115
msgid ""
"`maxCount: number` — soft cap on selections. iOS Photo Picker enforces this "
"when API supports; Android Photo Picker (API 33+) accepts a max in `[1, 10]`."
msgstr "`maxCount: number` —— 选择数量软上限。当 API 支持时，iOS 照片选择器会强制执行该限制；Android 照片选择器（API 33+）接受 `[1, 10]` 范围内的最大值。"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:118
msgid ""
"`allowMultiple: boolean` — if `false`, only one image can be picked "
"regardless of `maxCount`."
msgstr "`allowMultiple: boolean` —— 若为 `false`，无论 `maxCount` 如何，都只能选择一张图像。"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:120
msgid ""
"`callback(paths: string[])` — fires once when the user dismisses the picker. "
"`paths` is empty if the user cancelled."
msgstr "`callback(paths: string[])` —— 在用户关闭选择器时触发一次。如果用户取消，`paths` 为空。"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:127
msgid "`PHPickerViewController`"
msgstr "`PHPickerViewController`"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:127
msgid "None — the system picker doesn't require Photos permission"
msgstr "无 —— 系统选择器不需要 Photos 权限"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:128
msgid "**Android (API 33+)**"
msgstr "**Android (API 33+)**"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:128
msgid "`MediaStore.ACTION_PICK_IMAGES` (Photo Picker)"
msgstr "`MediaStore.ACTION_PICK_IMAGES`（照片选择器）"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:128
msgid "None — privacy-preserving"
msgstr "无 —— 保护隐私"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:129
msgid "**Android (API \\< 33)**"
msgstr "**Android (API \\< 33)**"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:129
msgid "`ACTION_GET_CONTENT` fallback"
msgstr "`ACTION_GET_CONTENT` 后备方案"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:129
msgid "`READ_MEDIA_IMAGES` (used only by the fallback path)"
msgstr "`READ_MEDIA_IMAGES`（仅在后备路径中使用）"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:130
msgid "`NSOpenPanel` filtered to image UTIs"
msgstr "`NSOpenPanel` 过滤为图像 UTI"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:131
msgid "**All other targets**"
msgstr "**所有其他目标**"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:131
msgid "No-op stub — `callback` invoked with `[]` immediately"
msgstr "空操作桩 —— `callback` 立即以 `[]` 调用"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:133
msgid ""
"On Android, picked URIs are copied into the app's cache dir (named "
"`perry_pick_<ms>_<idx>.<ext>` with the extension inferred from the MIME "
"type) so the absolute path returned is safe to read with `fs`."
msgstr "在 Android 上，所选 URI 会被复制到应用的缓存目录中（命名为 `perry_pick_<ms>_<idx>.<ext>`，扩展名根据 MIME 类型推断），因此返回的绝对路径可安全地用 `fs` 读取。"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:137
msgid "Image compression"
msgstr "图像压缩"

#: src/system/geolocation.md:139
msgid ""
"Pair the picker with the `sharp` package (compiled natively via Perry's well-"
"known bindings) to compress before upload:"
msgstr "将选择器与 `sharp` 包（通过 Perry 的 well-known 绑定原生编译）配合使用，在上传前压缩："

#: src/system/geolocation.md:142
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"import sharp from \"sharp\";\n"
"\n"
"const buf = await sharp(pickedPath)\n"
"  .resize({ width: 1600 })\n"
